data.description:
Welcome to this elegant home, where comfort meets sophistication. The spacious living area seamlessly connects to a stunning kitchen with exquisite granite countertops, a focal point for culinary delights. Two adjacent dining rooms offer versatility for formal dinners or casual brunches.

Ascend the staircase to discover a versatile loft, perfect for a home office or entertainment space. Three bedrooms, including a master with an en-suite bathroom, provide a serene retreat. Step into the well-appointed backyard, adorned with beautiful trees, creating a haven for outdoor enthusiasts. The expansive yard offers space for gardening, play, and entertaining, catering to various outdoor needs.

Conveniently located near shopping centers, a military base, and hospitals, this home harmoniously blends style, functionality, and accessibility. It's more than a house; it's a haven where thoughtful details create a luxurious living experience. Welcome home!
